<div class="nbunit" id="12Oct1932"><font color="red">12 October 1932</font> <i>NLPL</i> (to Paul L&eacute;on): &hellip; for the past 25 years I have refused to allow the detestable system of inverted commas or punctuation marks &hellip; to disfigure my pages &hellip; let them follow the French system </div>
